1
00:00:-03,-900 --> 00:00:01,120
字幕制作：大賬簿

2
00:00:28,530 --> 00:00:31,842
我叫阿希，是個奴隸
<i>My name is Ash. And I am a slave.</i>

3
00:00:35,365 --> 00:00:38,346
照我的判斷，現在是西元1300年...
<i>Close as I can figure it,</i>
<i>the year is 1300 AD...</i>

4
00:00:38,413 --> 00:00:40,914
...我被拖曳著踏上死亡路程
<i>... and I am being dragged to my death.</i>

5
00:00:41,093 --> 00:00:42,931
事情一開始不是這樣的
<i>It wasn't always like this.</i>

6
00:00:44,042 --> 00:00:45,983
我也有過真實的生活
<i>I had a real life once.</i>

7
00:00:47,928 --> 00:00:49,092
還有一份工作
<i>A job.</i>

8
00:00:55,634 --> 00:00:59,380
五金，12號走道
來美而廉，保證物美價廉
Hardware. Aisle 12.
Shop smart, shop S. Mart.

9
00:00:59,955 --> 00:01:02,959
我有個很好的女朋友，玲達
<i>I had a wonderful girlfriend, Linda.</i>

10
00:01:06,186 --> 00:01:09,498
我們一起開車到山上小屋渡假
<i>Together we drove to a small cabin</i>
<i>in the mountains.</i>

11
00:01:13,557 --> 00:01:16,538
有位考古學家來到這偏僻的地方...
<i>It seems an archeologist</i>
<i>had come to this remote place...</i>

12
00:01:16,606 --> 00:01:19,210
...致力翻譯與研究他的最新發現
<i>... to translate and study his latest find.</i>

13
00:01:20,290 --> 00:01:24,768
死亡志記
<i>Necronomicon ex Mortis.</i>
<i>The Book of the Dead.</i>

14
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:30,437
書本用人皮制成，以血液書寫...
<i>Bound in human flesh and inked in blood...</i>

15
00:01:30,676 --> 00:01:34,925
...這古籍記載了玄奇的埋葬儀式...
<i>... this ancient Sumerian text contained</i>
<i>bizarre burial rites...</i>

16
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:39,812
...咒語以及惡魔複活等文字
<i>... funerary incantations</i>
<i>and demon resurrection passages.</i>

17
00:01:41,196 --> 00:01:43,902
此書根本就不應存在人間
<i>It was never meant</i>
<i>for the world of the living.</i>

18
00:01:44,379 --> 00:01:47,223
它喚醒了樹林中的邪魔
<i>The book awoke something</i>
<i>dark in the woods.</i>

19
00:01:54,161 --> 00:01:55,599
玲達被抓走了
<i>It took Linda.</i>

20
00:01:56,775 --> 00:01:58,750
然後又來抓我
<i>And then it came for me.</i>

21
00:02:00,225 --> 00:02:05,205
邪魔進到我手裏
我只好斷腕自保
<i>It got into my hand and it went bad.</i>
<i>So I lopped it off at the wrist.</i>

22
00:02:11,482 --> 00:02:14,120
但它沒完沒了，又回來找我
<i>But that didn't stop it. It came back.</i>

23
00:02:16,876 --> 00:02:18,143
弄得天翻地覆
<i>Big time.</i>

24
00:02:35,569 --> 00:02:38,915
天啊！怎麼讓它停止？
For God's sake! How do you stop it?

25
00:03:00,830 --> 00:03:04,839
魔界英豪

26
00:03:35,873 --> 00:03:37,745
堵住他！
Surround the stranger!

27
00:03:50,781 --> 00:03:53,556
我這是...
Where the hell...

28
00:04:05,556 --> 00:04:08,696
別沖動，老大
我不知道怎麼來到這裏的
Easy now, chief.
I don't know how I got here.

29
00:04:09,342 --> 00:04:13,157
我也不想找麻煩
And I'm not looking for any trouble.

30
00:04:16,277 --> 00:04:18,013
這胄甲真堅固！
What a piece of armor this is!

31
00:04:19,694 --> 00:04:20,790
智者！
Wiseman!

32
00:04:26,528 --> 00:04:30,239
陛下，他一定就是志記裏提到的使者
My lord, I believe he is the one
written of in the Necronomicon.

33
00:04:30,716 --> 00:04:33,125
預言說到他將從天而降...
He who is prophesied to fall
from the heavens...

34
00:04:33,195 --> 00:04:35,673
...挽救我們於鬼怪之手
...and deliver us from
the terrors of the Deadites.

35
00:04:35,942 --> 00:04:37,678
什麼？那個傻子？
What? That buffoon?

36
00:04:38,019 --> 00:04:39,286
他...
Likely...

37
00:04:39,695 --> 00:04:42,104
...比較像亨利手下的人
...he's one of Henry's men!

38
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:45,814
跪下，混球！
Kneel, rapscallion!

39
00:04:47,132 --> 00:04:49,301
我說，把他丟進深坑裏！
I say, to the pit with him!

40
00:04:53,698 --> 00:04:56,907
-進坑！
-你這可憐的混球
. To the pit!
. You miserable bastard!

41
00:04:58,824 --> 00:05:00,320
別抓我
Get off of me!

42
00:05:02,744 --> 00:05:04,080
放開我！
Let me go!

43
00:05:12,661 --> 00:05:14,157
進城堡！
To the castle!

44
00:05:17,752 --> 00:05:21,224
抬起腳！別拖著！快！
Pick up your feet!
Stop dragging your feet! Come on!

45
00:05:21,404 --> 00:05:26,190
走，快點，快，快點
Move along. Come on, now.
Come on, pick it up.

46
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:29,133
嘗嘗這個的厲害
Have a taste of this!

47
00:05:36,011 --> 00:05:37,175
好了！
All right, you men!

48
00:05:37,284 --> 00:05:41,533
回到城堡後你將有個驚喜
You've got something to look forward to
when you get back to the castle!

49
00:05:42,276 --> 00:05:45,919
亞瑟王來到！開鐵門！
Lord Arthur approaches!
Raise the portcullis!

50
00:05:47,971 --> 00:05:51,888
亞瑟王！亞瑟王來到！
Lord Arthur! Lord Arthur approaches!

51
00:06:42,077 --> 00:06:46,292
亞瑟王，我兄弟呢？沒跟您一起嗎？
Lord Arthur, where is my brother?
Did he not ride with you?

52
00:06:46,499 --> 00:06:48,498
啊，驍勇善戰
Aye, and fought valiantly.

53
00:06:49,179 --> 00:06:52,217
但昨晚他在與亨利公爵一戰中捐軀了
But last night he fell in battle
to Duke Henry's men.

54
00:06:53,032 --> 00:06:54,470
很抱歉，席拉
I'm sorry, Sheila.

55
00:06:55,712 --> 00:06:57,711
-來
-你這白癡！
. Come on.
. You cretin!

56
00:06:58,761 --> 00:07:00,291
住手，雜種！
Stop it, you bastards!

57
00:07:01,843 --> 00:07:03,281
野蠻人！
Barbarians!

58
00:07:05,796 --> 00:07:08,331
住手！住手，你這雜種！
Stop it! Stop it, you little bastards!

59
00:07:08,409 --> 00:07:09,402
滾！
Beat it!

60
00:07:13,401 --> 00:07:14,839
鄙惡之人！
Foul thing!

61
00:07:15,612 --> 00:07:18,456
願神降罪於你！你是殺人凶手！
A pox on your throat!
Thou art a murderer!

62
00:07:18,895 --> 00:07:20,299
殺人凶手！
A bloody murderer!

63
00:07:25,562 --> 00:07:27,937
我要為我兄弟複仇！
My brother's death shall be avenged!

64
00:07:42,314 --> 00:07:44,449
團隊，候令！
Company, halt!

65
00:07:48,578 --> 00:07:50,142
除去他的項圈！
Get that yoke off him!

66
00:08:04,056 --> 00:08:06,934
你不是我的奴隸
You, sir, are not one of my vassals.

67
00:08:08,747 --> 00:08:10,151
你是誰？
Who are you?

68
00:08:11,091 --> 00:08:12,758
誰在問？
Who wants to know?

69
00:08:13,905 --> 00:08:17,149
我是紅衣亨利，薛爾公爵
I am Henry the Red. Duke of Shale.

70
00:08:17,524 --> 00:08:20,436
北陸之王，也是人民的領導者
Lord of the Northlands
and leader of its peoples.

71
00:08:21,377 --> 00:08:25,797
噢，哈囉，美褲先生
跟你說吧，老兄
Well, hello, Mister Fancy Pants.
I got news for you, pal.

72
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:29,072
現在你只領導兩樣事情
狗跟屎
You ain't leading but two things right now,
jack and shit.

73
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:32,122
-這裏沒狗
-閉上鳥嘴！
. And Jack left town.
. Shut your bleedin' hole!

74
00:08:32,465 --> 00:08:35,274
紳士們，亞瑟王！
Gentlemen, Lord Arthur!

75
00:08:43,856 --> 00:08:46,528
惡魔已蘇醒了
There is an evil awakened in this land.

76
00:08:47,541 --> 00:08:51,252
我的手下拼命抵抗...
And while my people fight
for their very souls against it...

77
00:08:51,461 --> 00:08:54,202
...你，紅衣亨利，向我們宣戰
...you, Henry the Red, wage war on us.

78
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,982
騙子！
Charlatan!

79
00:08:58,329 --> 00:09:01,310
是你先攻擊我們的
It was you who first turned
your swords on us.

80
00:09:01,378 --> 00:09:04,382
這個惡魔也已敗壞了我的手下！
And this evil has befouled
my people as well!

81
00:09:04,461 --> 00:09:07,601
你的手下也不見得比那深坑裏的...
Your people are no better
than the foul corruption...

82
00:09:07,676 --> 00:09:09,879
惡魔好多少...
...that lies in the bowels of that pit!

83
00:09:10,055 --> 00:09:11,927
對！你也好不了多少！
Right! You're no better!

84
00:09:12,132 --> 00:09:14,633
願神憐憫你的靈魂
May God have mercy upon your souls.

85
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:32,998
天啊！是什麼東西？
In God's name!
What hell. Spawned thing lurks there?

86
00:09:38,531 --> 00:09:42,140
把他丟進深坑去跟嗜血雜種作伴
Into the pit
with those bloodthirsty sons of whores.

87
00:09:42,719 --> 00:09:43,815
走！
Move!

88
00:09:44,495 --> 00:09:45,488
不！
No!

89
00:10:16,723 --> 00:10:19,361
天！天啊！
God! Heavenly God!

90
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:24,886
他逃走了！
He's escaping!

91
00:10:26,305 --> 00:10:27,801
抓住他！
Hold him!

92
00:11:02,186 --> 00:11:04,687
他們看起來沒那麼精明了吧？
They don't look so clever now, do they?

93
00:11:04,765 --> 00:11:06,432
他嚇壞了！
He's frightened!

94
00:11:09,456 --> 00:11:12,836
喂，喂！等等
Whoa, whoa! Wait a minute.

95
00:11:14,247 --> 00:11:16,416
等等，等一下！
Hold it. Wait a minute!

96
00:11:16,592 --> 00:11:18,659
你得了解，老兄
You gotta understand, man.

97
00:11:19,305 --> 00:11:22,217
我之前從沒見過這些混球！
I never even saw these assholes before!

98
00:11:23,158 --> 00:11:24,528
他嚇壞了！
He trembles!

99
00:11:26,442 --> 00:11:28,178
你在等什麼？
What are you waiting for?

100
00:11:28,585 --> 00:11:30,960
亨利，你得告訴他們，你不認識我
Henry, you gotta tell them
you don't know me.

101
00:11:31,668 --> 00:11:33,575
我們素未謀面，說啊！
We never met, tell them!

102
00:11:36,291 --> 00:11:38,700
他不會聽的，小兄弟
I do not think he'll listen, lad.

103
00:11:40,613 --> 00:11:44,828
聽清楚，你們抓錯人了
Look, I'm telling you.
You've got the wrong guy.

104
00:11:55,353 --> 00:11:58,391
跟你說你們抓錯人了
I'm telling you, you got the wrong guy.

105
00:13:14,853 --> 00:13:16,120
啊，你...
Why, you...

106
00:13:21,387 --> 00:13:26,035
-鐵釘
-他說鐵釘！上鐵釘！
. Spikes.
. Hey, he said spikes! Give him spikes!

107
00:13:40,315 --> 00:13:43,090
讓開！陌生人！
Make way! Strange one!

108
00:13:55,056 --> 00:13:56,084
陌生人！
Strange one!

109
00:14:21,388 --> 00:14:23,797
詛咒你
Damn you.

110
00:15:48,895 --> 00:15:51,338
你的鞋帶松了
You know, your shoelace is untied.

111
00:16:02,297 --> 00:16:03,633
好
All right.

112
00:16:05,412 --> 00:16:06,942
誰來挑戰？
Who wants some?

113
00:16:07,924 --> 00:16:09,557
該誰來？
Who's next?

114
00:16:11,844 --> 00:16:13,316
來啊？
How about it?

115
00:16:13,921 --> 00:16:18,341
誰來？誰要來挑戰？
Who wants some?
Who wants to have a little?

116
00:16:23,135 --> 00:16:24,128
你
You.

117
00:16:28,193 --> 00:16:29,860
你要打嗎？
You want some more?

118
00:16:34,458 --> 00:16:35,930
要嗎？
You want a little?

119
00:16:38,612 --> 00:16:41,250
你？要不要打？
Do you? You want some more?

120
00:16:58,345 --> 00:17:00,915
快滾
Now, get on those horses
and get out of here.

121
00:17:04,543 --> 00:17:05,947
放他們走！
Let them go!

122
00:17:29,468 --> 00:17:30,461
停！
Halt!

123
00:17:31,947 --> 00:17:34,220
謝謝你們的款待！
Thank you, generous hosts!

124
00:17:35,767 --> 00:17:37,365
拿劍的人！
Sword boy!

125
00:17:45,247 --> 00:17:48,958
驕傲的人，我要將你殺死
For that arrogance, I shall see you dead.

126
00:17:55,533 --> 00:17:56,765
巫術！
Sorcery!

127
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:00,616
好
Yeah.

128
00:18:01,663 --> 00:18:04,735
你們這些未開化的白癡們，聽好了
All right, you primitive screwheads,
listen up.

129
00:18:05,751 --> 00:18:07,155
看到這個？
See this?

130
00:18:08,163 --> 00:18:11,840
這是我的槍
This is my boom stick!

131
00:18:13,188 --> 00:18:17,437
12厘米，雙排雷敏頓槍
美而廉超市的頂尖貨色
It's a 12.gauge, double. Barreled Remington.
S. Mart's top of the line.

132
00:18:18,213 --> 00:18:20,748
可以在運動器材部門購買
You can find this
in the sporting goods department.

133
00:18:21,329 --> 00:18:24,573
沒錯，這把槍是在密西根州出品
That's right, this sweet baby was made
in Grand Rapids, Michigan.

134
00:18:24,981 --> 00:18:27,424
零售價是109.95美元
It retails for about $109.95.

135
00:18:27,930 --> 00:18:32,648
槍托是由核桃木做成
槍身由精鐵打造，配上靈敏板機
It's got a walnut stock,
cobalt. Blue steel, and a hair trigger.

136
00:18:33,323 --> 00:18:38,143
對啦，絕對物超所值
That's right. Shop smart. Shop S. Mart.

137
00:18:38,884 --> 00:18:40,482
懂了嗎？
You got that?

138
00:18:41,497 --> 00:18:43,267
我發誓...
Now, I swear...

139
00:18:44,211 --> 00:18:46,586
...你們誰要是敢...
...the next one of you primates...

140
00:18:47,260 --> 00:18:49,429
...再碰我一下...
...even touches me...

141
00:19:18,986 --> 00:19:23,532
來談談我該怎麼回去吧
Now, let's talk about how I get back home.

142
00:19:54,833 --> 00:19:57,242
我懇求您的寬恕，陛下
I prithee to forgive me, my Lord.

143
00:19:57,647 --> 00:20:00,148
我以為您是亨利的同黨
I believed thee one of Henry's men.

144
00:20:00,495 --> 00:20:03,567
一開始你要殺我，現在你要吻我
First you wanna kill me,
now you wanna kiss me.

145
00:20:05,252 --> 00:20:06,314
滾
Blow.

146
00:20:10,579 --> 00:20:13,423
怎麼樣？能不能送我回去？
So what's the deal?
Can you send me back or not?

147
00:20:13,494 --> 00:20:18,006
只有死亡志記才有能力
我們也在找這本邪惡的書
Only the Necronomicon has the power,
an unholy book which we also require.

148
00:20:18,284 --> 00:20:22,167
書中記載著如何讓你回到自己的時空
Within its pages are passages
that can send you back to your time.

149
00:20:22,372 --> 00:20:25,044
只有你，上天的使者，才能拿到它
Only you, the promised one,
can quest for it.

150
00:20:26,325 --> 00:20:29,363
我不要你的書，也不聽你廢話
I don't want your book.
I don't want your bullshit!

151
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:32,820
趕快把我送回我的時空
快！快！快...
Just send me back to my own time.
Pronto! Today! Chop...

152
00:20:43,109 --> 00:20:45,987
你該死
You shall die!

153
00:20:51,485 --> 00:20:54,729
你絕不可以拿死亡志記
You shall never take the Necronomicon.

154
00:20:55,438 --> 00:20:59,287
我們將飽餐你的靈魂
We shall feast upon your souls!

155
00:21:22,708 --> 00:21:25,049
那是魔法，拿斧頭來
It's a trick. Get an ax.

156
00:21:32,592 --> 00:21:34,499
守衛！殺死他！
Guards! Kill her!

157
00:21:35,942 --> 00:21:38,283
抓住巫婆！抓住她！
Capture the witch! Capture the witch!

158
00:21:39,057 --> 00:21:42,129
我的眼睛！我瞎了！天，我瞎了！
My eyes! I'm blind! Oh, God, I'm blind!

159
00:21:44,217 --> 00:21:45,210
不！
No!

160
00:21:50,749 --> 00:21:52,221
喂，妖女！
Yo, she. Bitch!

161
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,267
來啊
Let's go.

162
00:22:17,953 --> 00:22:20,762
如果死亡志記落在邪惡人手中...
If the Necronomicon fell into
the hands of the Deadites...

163
00:22:20,868 --> 00:22:23,438
...所有人類都會被惡魔消滅
...all mankind will be consumed
by this evil.

164
00:22:23,548 --> 00:22:25,957
現在你願意去取書了嗎？
Now will thou quest for the book?

165
00:22:39,864 --> 00:22:41,131
那個
That one.

166
00:23:08,374 --> 00:23:09,778
太棒了
Groovy.

167
00:23:23,315 --> 00:23:26,353
怎麼？你在農場長大的啊？
關上門
What's the matter, you raised in a barn?
Shut the door.

168
00:23:26,733 --> 00:23:29,873
大概是跟這些原始人一樣
都在農場長大的
Probably was raised in a barn,
with all the other primitives.

169
00:23:39,062 --> 00:23:42,134
智者說你是上天派遣來的
The Wisemen say that thou art
the promised one.

170
00:23:45,997 --> 00:23:48,909
據說你要去取書來幫助我們
'Tis said thou wilt journey for the book
to help us.

