懦夫
Coward.

342
00:54:10,308 --> 00:54:13,289
-救我！
-席拉！
. Help me!
. Sheila!

343
00:54:27,092 --> 00:54:29,570
別放箭！你會傷了她
Hold your arms! You'll hit the girl.

344
00:54:34,698 --> 00:54:35,965
拿劍來
My sword.

345
00:54:41,063 --> 00:54:42,330
可惡！
Damn you!

346
00:55:01,164 --> 00:55:02,636
挖，用力挖！
Dig, damn you!

347
00:55:03,945 --> 00:55:05,783
挖快點！
Dig faster!

348
00:55:06,055 --> 00:55:09,801
我將統領所有在戰斗中死去
滿身爬滿螻蟻的鬼東西
I shall command every worm. Infested
son of a bitch that ever died in battle.

349
00:55:09,875 --> 00:55:11,439
-謝謝您
-你！
. Thank you, sir.
. You there!

350
00:55:11,516 --> 00:55:13,149
很好！
Handsomely, now!

351
00:55:13,259 --> 00:55:16,068
我們去攻擊他們的城堡
拿回我的書
We shall storm their castle
and get my book.

352
00:55:16,474 --> 00:55:18,473
起來，你們這些惡棍
Hoist, you damnable varlets!

353
00:55:23,375 --> 00:55:26,619
歡迎回到活人的地盤
Welcome back to the land of the living.

354
00:55:27,329 --> 00:55:29,933
拿起鏟子來快挖！
Now pick up a shovel and get digging!

355
00:55:32,120 --> 00:55:33,821
把女人帶來！
Bring on the wench!

356
00:55:34,431 --> 00:55:35,961
下去！
Get down there!

357
00:55:45,855 --> 00:55:47,762
給我一個吻，寶貝
Give me some sugar, baby.

358
00:55:53,963 --> 00:55:57,744
你真是可愛啊？
Now ain't you the sweet little thing?

359
00:56:01,099 --> 00:56:03,977
別碰我，你這惡心的東西！
Don't touch me, you foul thing!

360
00:56:10,486 --> 00:56:13,695
來，乖
Come on. That's it.

361
00:56:27,672 --> 00:56:30,413
你要派上用場囉，快走！
We got plans for you, girly. Girl! Move!

362
00:56:32,228 --> 00:56:35,700
快拼命挖，快點！
Bust your bones, you dig up holes, dogs!
Get thee hence!

363
00:56:45,663 --> 00:56:47,399
有探子來報！
A scout approaches!

364
00:56:54,674 --> 00:56:56,170
牽著馬
Get his horse!

365
00:56:57,120 --> 00:56:58,250
起來
Arise.

366
00:56:58,326 --> 00:57:02,141
陛下，死亡軍團在野地上聚集
正朝著城堡過來
My Lord, an army of the dead gather
in the wilderness and approach the castle.

367
00:57:02,212 --> 00:57:04,655
-多遠？
-才兩天的路程
. How far from here?
. But two days ride.

368
00:57:04,792 --> 00:57:08,538
-有翅膀的是前鋒
-也許我們該快逃
. These winged ones are only the first.
. Perhaps we should leave soon.

369
00:57:08,611 --> 00:57:11,249
-到山中可保安全
-是，我們快逃！
. We'll be safe in the mountains.
. Yes. We must flee!

370
00:57:11,358 --> 00:57:14,396
-書上已記載了，這是注定的
-他們會奪走我們的靈魂
. It is written. It's been foretold.
. They'll take our souls.

371
00:57:14,508 --> 00:57:16,483
-我怕！
-所有人的靈魂！
. I'm afraid!
. Every one of our souls!

372
00:57:16,551 --> 00:57:18,218
我不想死
I don't want to die.

373
00:57:19,198 --> 00:57:23,173
好啊！快逃啊！
That's it! Go ahead and run!

374
00:57:24,223 --> 00:57:27,900
逃回家去跟媽媽哭啊！我？
Run home and cry to mama! Me?

375
00:57:29,382 --> 00:57:31,152
我不願再逃了！
I'm through running!

376
00:57:33,302 --> 00:57:35,837
我說我們留下來跟他們拼命
I say we stay here and fight it out.

377
00:57:36,384 --> 00:57:40,530
未來的人都跟你一樣會說大話嗎？
Are all men from the future
loudmouth braggarts?

378
00:57:40,941 --> 00:57:43,819
不，只有我才這樣
No. Just me, baby.

379
00:57:44,525 --> 00:57:45,495
只有我
Just me.

380
00:57:46,636 --> 00:57:50,108
我們如何在城堡牆邊抵抗死亡軍團？
How will we fight an army of the dead
at our castle walls?

381
00:57:50,488 --> 00:57:55,342
怎麼跟他們拼命？用說的嗎？
大部分的人都逃走了
How will you fight that? More words?
Most of our people have already fled.

382
00:57:55,581 --> 00:57:57,522
這裏只剩60個人
We are but 60 men.

383
00:57:58,731 --> 00:58:02,374
我們可以找紅衣亨利的人來幫忙
Then we'll get Henry the Red
and his men to fight with us.

384
00:58:04,995 --> 00:58:09,038
誰願意加入？
Now! Who's with me?

385
00:58:23,321 --> 00:58:25,125
我跟隨你
I'll stand by you.

386
00:58:27,374 --> 00:58:31,589
-我願意效力
-我會獻出勇氣！
. You can count on my steel.
. I'll offer up my courage!

387
00:58:31,931 --> 00:58:35,140
-我與你共進退！
-我站在你這邊！
. Me sword's by your side!
. I'm with you!

388
00:58:35,716 --> 00:58:37,749
我為你效力
I'll bend my bow to your will, sir.

389
00:58:42,149 --> 00:58:45,324
萬歲！萬歲！萬歲！
Hail! Hail! Hail!

390
00:59:02,216 --> 00:59:06,225
親愛的，跟大夥打個招呼
Well, my dear, say hello to the boys.

391
00:59:12,803 --> 00:59:15,281
很久沒見這麼美的人了
There's a sight for sore bones.

392
00:59:19,738 --> 00:59:24,456
我壞到骨頭裏了
I may be bad, but I feel good.

393
00:59:26,371 --> 00:59:29,009
-誰是統領？
-您，陛下
. Who rules?
. It is you, my lord.

394
00:59:29,119 --> 00:59:30,615
向城堡前進！
To the castle!

395
00:59:33,407 --> 00:59:35,245
-但大家都怕！
-太重了！夠了
. But the men are afraid!
. It's too heavy! Now, that's enough.

396
00:59:35,317 --> 00:59:37,486
別抱怨了！
Quit your bellyaching!

397
00:59:38,566 --> 00:59:42,746
我知道你們怕，我們都怕
I know you're scared. We're all scared.

398
00:59:44,262 --> 00:59:46,763
但這不表示我們怯懦
But that doesn't mean we're cowards.

399
00:59:47,444 --> 00:59:50,356
我們能打敗他們，一定能！
We can take these Deadites,
we can take them!

400
00:59:52,034 --> 00:59:53,438
運用科學
With science.

401
00:59:57,629 --> 00:59:59,501
快，快！
Hurry up, now!

402
01:00:00,208 --> 01:00:02,651
快！推，一起來！
Come on, fellas! Push! Heave ho!

403
01:00:16,457 --> 01:00:18,626
基礎化學

404
01:00:22,186 --> 01:00:23,990
蒸氣廠運作

405
01:00:54,817 --> 01:00:56,187
傾斜，傾斜
Tilt. Tilt.

406
01:00:57,564 --> 01:00:59,002
好，來，來
Okay, in, in.

407
01:01:08,217 --> 01:01:09,621
火藥

408
01:01:45,002 --> 01:01:48,543
來了！死亡軍團來了！
They're coming! The Deadites approach!

409
01:01:54,181 --> 01:01:57,630
快，你這些沒用的人！
他們就要到了！
Quickly now, you worthless fools!
They'll be on us anon!

410
01:01:57,767 --> 01:01:59,239
快！
Come on, guys!

411
01:02:03,529 --> 01:02:07,675
就要見真章了
你們最好別讓我失望
The moment of truth is almost here.
You men better not fail me now.

412
01:02:24,166 --> 01:02:26,369
他們聲勢如此浩大
There's so damned many of them.

413
01:02:39,879 --> 01:02:41,477
我需要多一點人手
I need more men.

414
01:03:24,636 --> 01:03:28,611
戰壘！堆起石頭！快！
Battle stations! Get those rocks up!
On the double!

415
01:03:28,992 --> 01:03:33,104
准備好彈弓！
讓他們知道我們的厲害！
Ready the catapults!
By God, let's give them what for!

416
01:03:42,829 --> 01:03:43,925
停！
Halt!

417
01:04:48,860 --> 01:04:51,532
-望遠鏡！
-遵命
. Looking glass!
. Aye, sire.

418
01:04:59,380 --> 01:05:01,823
拿到死亡志記後...
Once I possess the Necronomicon...

419
01:05:03,066 --> 01:05:08,080
...我會統治一切，你就是我的皇後
...I shall rule, and you shall be my queen.

420
01:05:22,564 --> 01:05:25,510
陛下，我們已經兩面都布置好了
My lord, we are positioned on both fronts.

421
01:05:25,579 --> 01:05:28,959
好，他們把我的書放哪裏？
Fine. Where are they keeping my book?

422
01:05:29,331 --> 01:05:32,209
那裏，陛下
在第二層牆的吊橋後面
There, my lord.
Beyond the drawbridge in the second wall.

423
01:05:32,279 --> 01:05:34,312
那是最安全的地方
That would be the safest place.

424
01:05:34,390 --> 01:05:39,108
沒有人能阻撓我取得死亡志記
I will not allow anything to keep me
from possessing that Necronomicon.

425
01:05:40,923 --> 01:05:45,172
現在，向城堡邁進
Now, bring me forth into that castle.

426
01:05:45,546 --> 01:05:48,755
-前進！
-前進！
. Forward!
. Forward!

427
01:05:48,896 --> 01:05:52,711
大肆破壞，放出戰狗！
Cry havoc, and let loose the dogs of war!

428
01:05:53,319 --> 01:05:56,231
攻向城堡！
To the castle!

429
01:06:00,320 --> 01:06:01,587
很好
Excellent.

430
01:06:04,642 --> 01:06:07,085
殺光活人！
Death to the mortals!

431
01:06:10,304 --> 01:06:11,502
箭！
Arrows!

432
01:06:12,079 --> 01:06:13,175
弓
Bows.

433
01:06:13,922 --> 01:06:15,018
上弦！
Load!

434
01:06:16,804 --> 01:06:17,866
滿弓！
Draw!

435
01:06:28,462 --> 01:06:30,129
火把！
Torch boy!

436
01:07:12,551 --> 01:07:13,749
穩住
Steady.

437
01:07:20,759 --> 01:07:21,855
發射！
Fire!

438
01:07:24,578 --> 01:07:27,284
前進，邪魔！前進！
Advance, you demons! Advance!

439
01:07:48,598 --> 01:07:51,510
對啦，寶貝！
Yeah, baby!

440
01:07:58,783 --> 01:08:00,119
好！
All right!

441
01:08:01,295 --> 01:08:04,001
-撤退！
-快逃啊！
. Retreat!
. Let's get the hell out of here!

442
01:08:14,295 --> 01:08:15,562
他真可惡！
Damn him!

443
01:08:16,439 --> 01:08:19,214
側面的第二突擊隊會成功的
The sortie on the second flank will stand.

444
01:08:19,386 --> 01:08:20,916
一定得成功！
It must!

445
01:08:22,301 --> 01:08:26,012
長官，南面有第二波的攻擊
Sire, there's a second division
approaching from the south.

446
01:08:26,657 --> 01:08:29,329
沖進城門！
Ram the gates!

447
01:08:33,725 --> 01:08:35,061
彈弓手！
Catapults!

448
01:08:35,502 --> 01:08:37,637
彈弓手！南面！
Catapults! South!

449
01:08:44,580 --> 01:08:48,463
-我們會擊敗他們！
-再度攻擊！
. We'll crush them!
. We'll strike again!

450
01:09:00,896 --> 01:09:02,392
發射！
Fire!

451
01:09:10,042 --> 01:09:11,344
哪來的火？
What the blazes?

452
01:09:19,489 --> 01:09:21,488
-小心！
-讓開！
. Watch out!
. Make way!

453
01:09:28,401 --> 01:09:29,771
快躲起來！
Seek cover!

454
01:09:39,389 --> 01:09:42,198
你們這些爛骨頭！
You miserable bags of bones!

455
01:09:42,372 --> 01:09:45,981
快爬起來再...
Pick yourselves up and sally for...

456
01:09:47,162 --> 01:09:48,498
再...
Sally for...

457
01:09:49,741 --> 01:09:51,740
再沖
Sally forth.

458
01:09:55,538 --> 01:09:57,845
快，你們這些沒用的東西！
Come on, you miserable wretches!

459
01:10:08,536 --> 01:10:09,632
前進！
Forward!

460
01:10:12,389 --> 01:10:14,890
鞏固城門！快！
Buttress that door! Now!

461
01:10:31,921 --> 01:10:33,085
石塊！
Rocks!

462
01:10:34,332 --> 01:10:35,496
可惡！
Damn you!

463
01:10:39,257 --> 01:10:41,358
一定很痛！
That's gotta hurt!

464
01:10:41,770 --> 01:10:43,140
混帳東西！
You cretins!

465
01:10:43,478 --> 01:10:44,676
箭！
Arrows!

466
01:10:45,891 --> 01:10:46,884
發射！
Fire!

467
01:10:52,357 --> 01:10:55,029
我們要讓那混帳好看！
We'll ram it down the bastard's throat!

468
01:10:56,478 --> 01:10:57,540
發射！
Fire!

469
01:11:03,044 --> 01:11:05,682
南面側攻隊，到西牆去！快！
South flank, to the western wall! Now!

470
01:11:06,260 --> 01:11:09,903
紅衣亨利呢？早告訴你他不會來！
Where is Henry the Red?
I told you he would not come!

471
01:11:09,978 --> 01:11:14,798
戴好你的罐頭帽子，鐵頭！
我說他會來，他就是會來！
Keep your sardine can on, bucket. Head!
I said he'll be here, he'll be here!

472
01:11:15,205 --> 01:11:17,911
我不認為，但我要告訴你
I think he will not. But know this.

473
01:11:18,321 --> 01:11:23,175
無論戰役結果如何
認為你是懦夫是我的錯
No matter how this battle fares,
I was wrong to think you a coward.

474
01:11:28,974 --> 01:11:31,783
沖破了！城陷了！
We've broken through! The castle is ours!

475
01:11:36,780 --> 01:11:39,452
殺光活人！
Kill the mortals!

476
01:11:44,217 --> 01:11:45,747
好了！
All right, men!

477
01:12:15,944 --> 01:12:19,290
他們沖破了第一道牆！
接下來怎麼辦？
They've breached the first wall!
What next?

478
01:12:26,296 --> 01:12:28,739
我們被遺棄了！
We are deserted!

479
01:12:29,780 --> 01:12:32,315
向後退！守衛城牆！
Fall back! Man the parapet!

480
01:12:32,728 --> 01:12:34,326
保護死亡志記！
Protect the book!

481
01:12:35,676 --> 01:12:37,240
願神救助
God save us all.

482
01:12:38,156 --> 01:12:42,039
爬上樓梯，小子！
到安全的牆後去！
Up the ladders, lads!
To the safety of the parapets!

483
01:12:52,060 --> 01:12:54,367
與21世紀打個招呼
Say hello to the 21st century.

484
01:13:07,538 --> 01:13:10,108
來！人人有份！
Come on! I got plenty for everybody!

485
01:13:19,097 --> 01:13:21,701
-滋味不錯吧？
-裝死！
. How do you like this?
. Play dead!

486
01:13:24,456 --> 01:13:26,865
抓住車上的人！
It's the one in the cart we want. Get him!

487
01:13:45,060 --> 01:13:47,093
再見啦，蠢蛋！
<i>Sayonara</i>, sucker!

488
01:13:53,737 --> 01:13:54,901
你...
Why, you...

489
01:13:56,920 --> 01:13:59,398
你逃不出我的手掌心！
You can run, but you can't hide!

490
01:14:25,799 --> 01:14:26,997
席拉？
Sheila?

491
01:14:52,399 --> 01:14:54,900
-我們已拿下庭院了，陛下
-很好
. We've secured the courtyard, my lord.
. Excellent.

492
01:14:55,783 --> 01:14:58,558
該是拿書的時候了，把牆撞破！
Now I will have that book.
Storm the walls!

493
01:14:59,032 --> 01:15:00,128
樓梯！
Ladders!

494
01:15:00,205 --> 01:15:04,088
來，你們這些死人骨頭！快！
不然我送你們進沾膠廠！
Come on, you bony devils! Hurry up!
Or I'll send you to the glue factory!

495
01:15:04,158 --> 01:15:05,322
強力膠！
Elmer!

496
01:15:06,135 --> 01:15:07,607
往牆進攻！
To the walls!

497
01:15:10,892 --> 01:15:13,496
我把你切成一片片的！不，不！
I'll slice you to ribbons! No, no!

498
01:15:38,330 --> 01:15:40,066
慢著！小心！
Wait! Look out!

499
01:15:47,610 --> 01:15:50,785
-嘿，你是我的人，甜心！
-走開！
. Hey, you're mine, sweetie!
. Get off of her!

500
01:15:57,996 --> 01:15:59,263
可惡！
Damn you!

501
01:15:59,972 --> 01:16:04,552
守護死亡志記，小子們！
否則就死在惡魔的火裏
Defend the Necronomicon, lads!
Or perish in the devil's fire!

502
01:16:09,253 --> 01:16:11,959
-陛下
-看好志記！
. My lord.
. Stay with the book!

503
01:16:12,167 --> 01:16:14,039
志記會是我們的！
The book will be ours!

504
01:16:36,590 --> 01:16:37,618
嗨！
Hello!

505
01:16:48,182 --> 01:16:49,815
這書是我的！
The book is mine!

506
01:16:54,413 --> 01:16:55,885
拿去！
There you go!

507
01:17:04,263 --> 01:17:06,262
我把你剁個稀巴爛
I'll cut your gizzard out.

508
01:17:07,278 --> 01:17:08,750
去哪了？
Where'd he go?

509
01:17:19,942 --> 01:17:21,414
來吧！
Come to Papa!

510
01:17:22,689 --> 01:17:23,921
去抓他！
Get him!

511
01:17:54,147 --> 01:17:58,533
瘋女人，走開！
你要把我眼睛挖出來了！
Crazy bitch, get off me!
You're tearing my eyes out!

512
01:17:59,809 --> 01:18:01,145
妖女！
You witch!

513
01:18:08,050 --> 01:18:09,020
對
Right.

514
01:18:16,627 --> 01:18:18,762
你以前認為我很美的
You found me beautiful once.

515
01:18:19,441 --> 01:18:21,976
蜜糖，你變成醜八怪了
Honey, you got real ugly.

516
01:18:41,418 --> 01:18:42,982
在這
There we are.

517
01:18:51,937 --> 01:18:53,775
你要來狠的？
You wanna play rough?

518
01:19:05,171 --> 01:19:06,403
好！
All right!

519
01:19:29,896 --> 01:19:31,563
你慘了！
You're going down!

520
01:19:32,676 --> 01:19:35,177
-我往上走！
-我追你到底！
. I'm going up!
. I'm coming for you!

521
01:20:06,714 --> 01:20:07,844
抓他！
Get him!

522
01:20:10,299 --> 01:20:11,463
借過！
Excuse me!

523
01:20:11,605 --> 01:20:13,443
來！對！
Come on! All right!

524
01:20:16,061 --> 01:20:19,133
你激怒我的，你這醜八怪！
You're pissin' me off,
you ugly son of a bitch!

525
01:20:21,891 --> 01:20:22,884
不！
No!

526
01:20:41,422 --> 01:20:44,300
我要把你毀容了！
I'll spoil those good looks!

527
01:20:47,419 --> 01:20:48,891
暗箭傷人！
Backstabber!

528
01:20:54,454 --> 01:20:55,824
別動！
Hold still!

529
01:21:10,837 --> 01:21:12,904
來囉！
Tallyho!

530
01:21:20,385 --> 01:21:25,171
-我們守不下去了！
-一定要守！要保護志記！
. We can't hold the battlements!
. We will hold! We must protect the book!

531
01:21:25,444 --> 01:21:28,048
紅衣亨利呢？他怎麼還...
Where's Henry the Red? Why's he not...

532
01:21:29,833 --> 01:21:32,276
我們被遺棄了！
We are deserted!

533
01:21:33,685 --> 01:21:35,352
我們勢力薄弱！
We're overwhelmed!

534
01:21:57,606 --> 01:21:59,845
我要跟你沒完沒了
I got a bone to pick with you.

535
01:22:00,520 --> 01:22:01,718
來！
Come on!

536
01:22:08,795 --> 01:22:10,930
我把你剁個稀巴爛！
I'll slice your gizzard open!

537
01:22:28,126 --> 01:22:29,656
落在我手裏了！
Now you're mine!

538
01:22:36,736 --> 01:22:37,729
不！
No!

539
01:22:51,510 --> 01:22:52,503
你-
Why, you<i>...</i>

540
01:22:52,582 --> 01:22:56,899
放下劍！
一有機會我就把你喉嚨給割了
Let go of the sword!
I'll cut your throat out if I get the chance.

541
01:23:19,719 --> 01:23:21,317
我拿到書了！
I have the book!

542
01:23:27,525 --> 01:23:29,329
拿到死亡志記了！
I possess the Necronomicon!

543
01:23:29,401 --> 01:23:33,352
我打敗你的軍隊了！
現在我要複仇了！
I've crushed your pathetic army!
Now I'll have my vengeance!

544
01:23:33,421 --> 01:23:37,338
紅衣！紅衣！
亨利公爵帶人來援救了
The Red! The Red!
Duke Henry and his men have come!

545
01:23:37,441 --> 01:23:41,792
為國王和城堡，高呼萬歲！
For king and castle! Cry havoc!

546
01:23:42,466 --> 01:23:47,252
拳頭、血和死亡！
Blows, blood, and death!

547
01:23:51,043 --> 01:23:52,641
我們有救了！
We are saved!

548
01:24:03,539 --> 01:24:07,616
向前沖，兄弟們！
他們在撤退了
Onward, valiant cousins!
Their ranks are broke!

549
01:24:09,034 --> 01:24:10,438
真倒楣！
Bloody hell!

550
01:24:11,345 --> 01:24:15,628
你毀了我統治的計劃！
你領死吧！
You've spoiled my plan for conquest!
And now you're going to die!

551
01:24:16,304 --> 01:24:19,513
坐穩了，死人骨頭！
你馬上要起飛了！
Buckle up, bonehead!
Because you're going for a ride!

552
01:24:34,930 --> 01:24:36,528
勝利在握！
Victory is ours!

553
01:25:03,542 --> 01:25:06,991
-如果你要作戰-
-嗯，開始吧！
. lf it's a fight you want<i>...</i>
. Well, start something!

554
01:25:07,394 --> 01:25:10,398
-站好，小子們！
-我們准備好了！
. Stand ready, lads!
. We're ready for you!

555
01:26:02,506 --> 01:26:04,036
走開，小子
Move yourself, lad.

556
01:26:04,381 --> 01:26:05,979
-你的手
-嘿，亨利
. Your hand, man.
. Hey, Henry.

557
01:26:06,057 --> 01:26:08,032
-你已償還債務了
-害我們捏一把冷汗
. The debt's paid.
. You had us going.

558
01:26:08,100 --> 01:26:09,436
-女士
-亞瑟
. Milady.
. Arthur.

559
01:26:09,507 --> 01:26:12,213
-我們勝利了，朋友！
-我們勝利了！
. Well won, my friend.
. We've won the day!

560
01:26:18,821 --> 01:26:23,001
我們是手足了！
新的王國誕生了！
We're brothers now!
A new kingdom shall be born!

561
01:26:26,091 --> 01:26:30,306
書上說
一滴甘露會使人睡上一個世紀
The book tells us that each drop
allows a man to sleep for a century.

562
01:26:31,049 --> 01:26:35,161
飲下六滴，你就會在自己的時空醒來
Swallow six drops,
thou shall awaken in thine own time.

563
01:27:39,796 --> 01:27:41,566
願神降福於你
God bless you, sire.

564
01:28:23,247 --> 01:28:24,880
六滴
Six drops.

565
01:28:27,904 --> 01:28:32,255
1，2，3，4...
One, two, three, four...

566
01:28:33,298 --> 01:28:34,291
...5
...five.

567
01:28:42,511 --> 01:28:43,915
5
Five.

568
01:28:45,426 --> 01:28:46,396
6
Six.

569
01:30:04,825 --> 01:30:06,195
我到家了
I'm home.

570
01:30:25,797 --> 01:30:27,669
人工制品！
Manufactured products!

571
01:30:41,711 --> 01:30:44,715
天！不！不！
God! No! No!

572
01:30:45,028 --> 01:30:47,666
我睡過頭了！
I slept too long!
